  coach_language = 'Primary subrole: conditioning_circuit. Belongs in Sustained Capacity because the intended stress is repeatable wall-ball work under fatigue while maintaining posture, breathing, target accuracy, and safe mechanics. Coach wall-ball work by phase intent: skill reps stay crisp, power reps stay fresh, support drills stay controlled, and conditioning stops when quality drops.',
